<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880405-0098 </DOCNO><HL> CVB Investor Files Stake Equal to 5.1% </HL><SO> </SO><CO> CVBF </CO><IN> TNM </IN><DATELINE> WASHINGTON  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Ronald O. Kruse, an Ontario, Calif., investor, said he holds the equivalent of a 5.1% stake in CVB Financial Corp.'s common shares outstanding.    In a Securities and Exchange Commission filing, Mr. Kruse said he controls 115,489 CVB common shares, assuming the exercise of options.    According to the filing, Mr. Kruse holds his CVB stock for investment purposes.    Mr. Kruse is an outside CVB director. CVB, an Ontario, Calif.-based bank holding company, declined to comment on the filing. </TEXT></DOC>